text: Drue Wawrzynski is an American water polo player. She played for the United States women's national water polo team. She participated at the 2005 World Aquatics Championships, winning the silver medal. She played for California State University, Long Beach's women's volleyball team. == References == Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:American water polo players
